0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015414, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Lord of the month of Ramadhan, and whatever of the Quran and blessings You sent down during it I ask You to bestow Your Blessings on Muhammad and his Progeny and bless me with the love for prayer, fasting, Hajj, Umrah and visiting my relatives loving what You Love and despising what You dislike.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA RABBA SHAHRE RAMAZAANA WA MAA ANZAL-TA FEEHE MINAL QUR-AANE WAL BARA-KAATE AS-ALOKA AN TO-SALLE-YA A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WA AN TAR-ZUQA-NEE HUBBAS SALAATE WAS-SEYAAME WAL HAJJE WAL OO’MRA-TE WA SELAA-TIR RAHE-ME WA TO-HABBE-BA ILAIY-YA KULLA MAA AH-BABTA WA TO-BAGH-GHEZA ILAIY-YA KULLA MAA AB-GHAZ-TA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ رَبَّ شَهْرِ رَمَضَانَ وَمَا اَنْزَلْتَ فِيْهِ مِنَ الْقُرْآنِ وَالْبَرَكَاتِ اَسْئَلُكَ اَنْ تُصَلِّيَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاَنْ تَرْزُقَنِيْ حُبَّ الصَّلَاةِ وَالصِّيَامِ وَالْحَجِّ وَالْعُمْرَةِ وَصِلَةِ الرَّحِمِ وَتُحَبِّبَ اِلَيَّ كُلَّ مَا اَحْبَبْتَ وَتُبَغِّضَ اِلَيَّ كُلَّ مَا اَبْغَضْتَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "Arabi