th O the Most Compassionate, Most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNA-KA TA-KAFFAL-TA BE-RIZQEE WA RIZQE KULLE DAAB-BATIN YAA KHAIRA MAD-OO’WIN WA YAA KHAIRA MAS-OO-LIN WA YAA KHAIRA MURTA-JAN WA AW-SA-A’ MAN A’TAA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WAR-ZUQ-NIS SA-A’TA WADDA’TA WAS-SA-AA’DATA FEE HAA-ZASH SHAH-RIL A’ZEEME YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّكَ تَكَفَّلْتَ بِرِزْقِيْ وَرِزْقِ كُلِّ دَابَّةٍ يَا خَيْرَ مَدْعُوٍّ وَيَا خَيْرَ مَسْئُوْلٍ وَيَا خَيْرَ مُرْتَجًى وَاَوْسَعَ مَنْ اَعْطٰى صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَارْزُقْنِي السَّعَةَ وَالدَّعَةَ وَالسَّعَادَةَ فِيْ هٰذَا الشَّهْرِ الْعَظِيْمِ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, 